      "span_text": "Social tourism is also linked to debates in sustainable tourism due to the fact it takes a more holistic approach relating to the ethics underpinning sustainable tourism, and for the ways in which it is framed as a more responsible form of tourism  , contrasted with the more morally circumspect practices of the global tourism industry."
